                <div style="width: 100%; height: 48px; border: 2px dashed #006AFF; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: rgba(0, 106, 255, 0.05); color: #006AFF; font-weight: 600;">12px all</div>
